27) $A=\left(\begin{array}{ccc}2 & 4 & 8 \\ 2 & 5 & 12 \\ 0 & 1 & 6\end{array}\right) \sim\left(\begin{array}{lll}2 & 4 & 8 \\ 0 & 1 & 4 \\ 0 & 1 & 6\end{array}\right)(\because 1$ 행 $\times(-1)+2$ 행 $\rightarrow 2$ 행 $)$
$$\sim\left(\begin{array}{lll}
2 & 4 & 8 \\
